# Copy to .env.local — OPENAI_API_KEY, Supabase, wallet keys, etc.

# ── Browserless.io (recommended for deployment) ──────────────────────────────
# Hosted browser with residential proxy, video recording, and stealth mode.
# Sign up at https://browserless.io — get your API token from the dashboard.
# When set, all Playwright sessions run on Browserless instead of locally.
# BROWSERLESS_TOKEN=your_api_token_here
